= Requirements =

{{box title="TL;DR: The Rules of FactHarbor"}}
🎯 **Goal**: Translate user needs into a verifiable, automated system.
⚖️ **Philosophy**: **System-over-data**—we fix the algorithm, not the individual output.
{{/box}}

