== 🎨 Visual Reference: The User Experience ==

Requirements are best understood through the intended user experience. Below are the key UI patterns defined by these requirements.

=== 1. Side-by-Side Analysis (FR12) ===
Provides an immediate comparison between the source document and FactHarbor's evidence-based findings.

=== 2. In-Article Highlighting (FR13) ===
Real-time credibility indicators overlayed on the text.

(% class="box successmessage" style="margin:10px 0;" %)
(((
🟢 **Researchers found that Mediterranean diet followers had a 25% lower risk of heart disease**
↑ WELL SUPPORTED • 87% confidence
)))

(% class="box warningmessage" style="margin:10px 0;" %)
(((
🟡 **Some experts believe this diet can completely prevent heart attacks**
↑ UNCERTAIN • 45% confidence — Overstated based on evidence
)))

